{"tid":2012149,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】廣告公司推「紙皮病床」 可變身棺材解決短缺問題","createTime":"2020-05-11T12:40:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T13:41:11.000Z","uid":173200,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0954e909fb3da88ee79efc5d8101c0f0d79a0cb1","tid":2012149,"uid":173200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:40:10.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎在南美洲哥倫比亞造成逾萬人感染及逾400人死亡。面對當地及鄰國出現病床及棺材短缺，首都波哥大一間廣告公司設計出可以變成棺材的「紙皮病床」，望一次過解決病床和棺材不足的問題。<br />\n<br />\nABC Displays是一間廣告公司，他們設計的紙皮病床附有金屬圍欄，倘若病人不幸病逝，病床就可以變為紙棺材。公司經理戈麥斯（Rodolfo G&oacute;mez）指，他目睹鄰國厄瓜多爾疫情爆發後，海岸城市瓜亞基爾（Guayaquil）因為死者太多，殯儀館無法接收遺體，導致不少家庭有親友過世後，遺體要放在家中或家門外幾日，情況淒涼，激發他想辦法紓緩棺材短缺的問題。戈麥斯說：「貧窮家庭買不起一口棺材。」厄瓜多爾至今有逾2.8萬宗確診及1,700人死亡。<br />\n<br />\nABC Displays在全國封鎖抗疫期間沒有生意，公司上下利用這段時間想出紙皮病床。戈麥斯指他們與私人診所合作設計新床，希望這些病床可以用於急救診所。病床可以負重149公斤（330磅），每個大約85美元（663港元），戈麥斯展示病床時，還讓幾位員工一起坐在床上，以示病床堅固，他打算向資源短缺的亞馬遜省捐出10張新床，但目前未知當局會否使用這些紙皮病床，公司也未有收到訂單。<br />\n<br />\n不過，至少有一名醫生質疑紙皮病床是否足夠堅固，他同時警告遺體要先用密封袋包好，才可以放入紙棺材內，避免疾病傳播。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/M2KQGRUiKKxk2jBq1lBQa2FBW14=/802x451/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/AEIDNQ6ZFAIHROJRADQGDBVOME.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FM2KQGRUiKKxk2jBq1lBQa2FBW14%3D%2F802x451%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FAEIDNQ6ZFAIHROJRADQGDBVOME.jpg&h=34ffb753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200510/large/1589090186_29c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200510%2Flarge%2F1589090186_29c3.jpg&h=f775bef6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200510/large/1589090186_6c31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200510%2Flarge%2F1589090186_6c31.jpg&h=d9ed9dfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSourse: <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200511/H3UFXL5ZS2JS2W3UNXJEFMMSGE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200511%2FH3UFXL5ZS2JS2W3UNXJEFMMSGE%2F&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HTrpXFO54mr1mpDNnesGdkc%3D&h=7d02f98b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200511%2FH3UFXL5ZS2JS2W3UNXJEFMMSGE%2F&h=217316f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200511/H3UFXL5ZS2JS2W3UNXJEFMMSGE/</a>"},{"pid":"adf2a56c133b65280bff5f1bfc32ae9e68d14caa","tid":2012149,"uid":74567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:41:11.000Z","msg":"唔出奇 紙皮連道場都整到"}]}